OL,3,CWhy is the Middle East conflict
OL,4,Cpushing up energy prices in the UK?
OL,6,FWords by Rhys Nelson
OL,8,FHousehold energy bills are forecast to
OL,9,Frise by 10% from July following sharp
OL,10,Fincreases in wholesale gas prices
OL,11,Fdriven by the escalating conflict in
OL,12,Fthe Middle East, experts have warned.
OL,14,FBut some UK drivers are already
OL,15,Fcomplaining of petrol stations running
OL,16,Fout of fuel now as the war in the
OL,17,Fregion continues to escalate.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
