OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772676194
OL,3,CWhy is the Middle East conflict
OL,4,Cpushing up energy prices in the UK?
OL,6,FSo why is the conflict pushing up
OL,7,Fenergy prices, and can we expect
OL,8,Fpetrol and diesel prices to go up? ITV
OL,9,FNews explains.
OL,11,FWhy is this happening?
OL,13,FOil markets are influenced by several
OL,14,Fglobal factors, including economic
OL,15,Fgrowth, supply and demand, and
OL,16,Fgeopolitics.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
