CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772676194
OL,3,CWhy is the Middle East conflict
OL,4,Cpushing up energy prices in the UK?
OL,6,FUncertainty around the supply and
OL,7,Favailability of the commodity means
OL,8,Fthe cost of buying it will go up.
OL,9,FTherefore, conflicts and political
OL,10,Ftensions can drive price changes.
OL,12,FEarlier this week, Iran issued
OL,13,Fwarnings that it would strike ships
OL,14,Fpassing through the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,15,Fwhich is one of the most critical
OL,16,Fpassageways for oil shipments in the
OL,17,Fworld.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
