PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772676194
OL,3,CWhy is the Middle East conflict
OL,4,Cpushing up energy prices in the UK?
OL,6,FIt's located at the southern end of
OL,7,Fthe Persian Gulf and sees around 20%
OL,8,Fof the world's oil supply pass through
OL,9,Fit.
OL,11,FAn adviser to the paramilitary
OL,12,FRevolutionary Guard, Brigadier General
OL,13,FEbrahim Jabbari, declared this week
OL,14,Fthat the strait "is closed" and vowed
OL,15,Fto set fire to any ships that passed
OL,16,Fthrough it.
OL,18,FThis caused tanker traffic to stall,
OL,19,Fwith reports suggesting that sea
OL,20,Ftraffic in the area fell by around 80%.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
