OL,3,CWhy is the Middle East conflict
OL,4,Cpushing up energy prices in the UK?
OL,6,FConsequently, oil prices spiked on
OL,7,FMonday over concerns that a prolonged
OL,8,Fdisruption of crude supplies in the
OL,9,Fregion could raise energy costs.
OL,11,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FDonald Trump has suggested the US Navy
OL,17,Fcould escort oil tankers and other
OL,18,Fvessels through the Strait of Hormuz
OL,19,Fif needed to balance out oil supply,
OL,20,Fthough questions remain around whether
OL,21,Fthis will take place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
