OL,3,CWhy is the Middle East conflict
OL,4,Cpushing up energy prices in the UK?
OL,6,FRising oil costs mean it will cost
OL,7,Fmore to transport and ship products,
OL,8,Fwhich, coupled with disruptions to
OL,9,Fsupply routes, could filter through to
OL,10,Fprices at the till in the months to
OL,11,Fcome.
OL,13,FCrude oil is also used in many
OL,14,Ffertilizers, which are used to grow
OL,15,Ffood and are vital to the global food
OL,16,Fchain. Without them, crop yields would
OL,17,Fdecline sharply. Around a quarter of
OL,18,Fthe fertilizer used to grow food has
OL,19,Fto travel through the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
