PN,30914
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1772676194
OL,3,CWhy is the Middle East conflict
OL,4,Cpushing up energy prices in the UK?
OL,6,FThe countries currently affected by
OL,7,Fconflict are also significant
OL,8,Fproducers of dates, olive oil, nuts
OL,9,Fand spices such as saffron.
OL,11,FAll of this depends on how long the
OL,12,Fconflict goes on for. Some experts say
OL,13,Fthat if it's short-lived, the economy
OL,14,Fcould weather the storm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
